Package: tip
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Clustering Using the Table Invitation Prior (TIP)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Charles W. Harrison, Qing He, Hsin-Hsiung Huang
Description: Cluster data without specifying the number of clusters using the Table Invitation Prior (TIP). TIP is a Bayesian prior that uses pairwise distance and similarity information to cluster vectors, matrices, or tensors.
Maintainer: Charles W. Harrison <charleswharrison@knights.ucf.edu>
